(3, 0, 2, 'Processor', 'default.jpg', '<h3>Find the Latest Processor Price in BD from Our Website</h3><p><br></p><p>The processor is a mobilized circuit that generally performs the predictions that run a computer. A processor is a central processing unit called the main processor in a computer\'s electric circuit. The processing unit helps introduction with the computer program. Its work performs arithmetically. Processor prices in Bangladesh like intel processor price or core i3 processor price depend on the international market if they can\'t input the process, then it rare to the market and its price much. It\'s the real job to receive input and process this data and provide the appropriate output. The most popular processor manufactures are in the microprocessor is a multifunction worker. The first microprocessor came to market in 1970, and this name is \"Intel 4004\" Microprocessors have the 5th generation.</p>', 'processor', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(4, 3, 2, 'Intel', 'default.jpg', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;\">About Intel Processor:</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Intel Corporation is one of the chip manufacturing companies in the world. Intel produces platform products that incorporate various components &amp; technologies such as a microprocessor &amp; chip, a stand-alone SoC, or a multichip package. It has dominated the PC chip market through its processors such as the Intel Core processor family &amp; the Intel quark, Intel Quark, Intel Atom, Celeron, Pentium, Intel Xeon. The three engineers from Fairchild Semiconductor created Intel in Mountain View, California, to develop silicon-based chips in 1968.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Intel has been producing Core X-series Processors, Core i9 Processors, Core i7 processors, Corei5 Processors, Core i3 Processors Etc.</p>', 'intel-processor', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(5, 3, 2, 'AMD', 'default.jpg', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;\">About AMD Processor:</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Generally, a computer processor is known as a microprocessor. It is a small chip placed in the computers and other electronic components to process the tusks. Processors can do all the tusks or instructions such as logical, arithmetical, input/output (I/O) &amp; other basic instructions given by humans &amp; created by hardware or operating system. The main job of a processor is to collect commands from input devices and convey the results to the output devices. . Nowadays, there are more advanced modern processors available in the market &amp; they are capable of controlling trillions of instructions per second. A computer\'s central processing unit-CPU, controls the action and data flow in the computer in no time. At present, Intel® and AMD® are two major manufacturers of computer processors in the world.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 'amd-processor', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(6, 0, 2, 'Motherboard', 'default.jpg', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;\">Gigabyte Perform Better:</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">GIGABYTE has actually used better covered flat chokes. Not only does this secure the chokes from damage, but however it also safeguards the various other bordering parts on the motherboard from magnetic flux leaks from the choke, thus boosting the security of the motherboard. Such An Example Gigabyte Motherboard is H370 AORUS Video Gaming.</p>', 'motherboard', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(7, 6, 2, 'Gigabyte', 'default.jpg', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;\">Gigabyte Perform Better:</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">GIGABYTE has actually used better covered flat chokes. Not only does this secure the chokes from damage, but however it also safeguards the various other bordering parts on the motherboard from magnetic flux leaks from the choke, thus boosting the security of the motherboard. Such An Example Gigabyte Motherboard is H370 AORUS Video Gaming.</p>', 'gigabyte-motherboard', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(8, 0, 2, 'Graphics Card', 'default.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(61, 61, 61); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">Original store BD always sells the MSI Graphics Card available at the best price in BD for giving you a smooth experience like never before. We have almost all MSI graphics cards available in the market. So you can buy an MSI graphics card from the original store ltd. At a competitive market price in BD to make your PC up-to-date. If you need any inquiry about MSI graphics card for PC or if you won\'t know the latest MSI graphics card price, visit our website or visit any of our branches across Dhaka city.</span><br></p>', 'graphics-card', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL),
(9, 8, 2, 'MSI', 'default.jpg', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;\">About MSI Graphics Card:</h2><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">MSI is an industry-leading &amp; well-reputed manufacturing brand in the laptop &amp; computer accessories Arena. They manufacture, design, develop market graphics cards, Desktop PC, monitors, Mainboards, Computer storage &amp; Accessories. MSI was established in 200. The product line-up has a solid-state drive (SSD), Graphics Cards, motherboards, Desktop PC, Monitor, Case, liquid Cooler, Power supply &amp; other peripherals, and Components. In addition, MSI manufacture NVIDIA GPU &amp; AMD GPU graphics cards &amp; MSI graphics cards deliver lighting fast, smooth gaming experience.</p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\">GeForce RTX™ 3070 VENTUS 3X 8G OC LHR, GeForce RTX™ 3070 VENTUS 3X 8G LHR, GeForce RTX™ 3070 VENTUS 3X 8G LHR, GeForce RTX™ 3070 VENTUS 2X 8G OC LHR, GeForce RTX™ 3070 VENTUS 2X 8G LHR are some of the models of MSI graphics card.</p>', 'msi-graphics-card', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL);

